The Perfect Match: Warres Otima Port & Godiva
List.Description:
Love and romance truly radiates in this gift. The renowned Port House Warres, Otima is a 10 year tawny Port made in a lighter, more contemporary style. Beautifully packaged in our gift box designed with cascading hearts, this Port is exceptional when paired with Godiva's 8-piece ballotin of assorted creamy milk, white and dark chocolates.

Each gift set contains:

  • Warres Otima 10 Year Tawny Port (500ml)
  • Godiva 8 pc Gold Ballotin Gift Box
  • Complimentary Hearts Gift Box

Wine gift sets & baskets may be packaged with the bottles separately boxed for their protection during shipment

Pursuant to state laws in New York, gifts that contain both food and wine will be sent in two separate packages.

Laguiole Waiter's Corkscrew
List.Description: The Chateau Laguiole Corkscrew is a beautiful gift that will be treasured by any wine lover. Hand made by Laguiole in the ancient knife making center of Thiers France, this authentic corkscrew was designed by Master Sommelier Guy Vialis and is a prestige statement for any wine professional. Corkscrew includes a long, forged knife blade, a smooth, rounded boot lever, and a long spiral. Handle is made of natural black horn which has been polished to a smooth finish. Leather case included.
